Link to Chicago LDC Forum PresentationsDear Patrice Here is the link for the presentations from the recently completed LDC Forum Gas Storage Strategies and Market Center Hubs September in Chicago We hope that by making copies available to you in this format you will get additional valueinformation from the Forum Click here presentationshtm to see a listing of the speakers and then click on each presentation you would like to review Thank you for your support of this Forum and God Bless America Jerry Ribnick The Interchange Energy Group
